NeuralNetwork.Components

Class Neuron

  • java.lang.Object
    • NeuralNetwork.Components.Neuron

  • public class Neuron
extends java.lang.Object
    The Neuron is the smallest unit at the neural network. It saves all connections to the next layes neurons, its value and its error (backpropagation)
